  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety Study of BDB-001 in Severe COVID-19 With ALI/ARDS</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-center, Open-label, Randomized Parallel Controlled Evaluation on the Efficacy and Safety of BDB-001 Injection in the Treatment of Progressive Severe COVID-19 in Phase II/III</official_title>
