  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This multi-center, open, randomized study will evaluate the efficacy and safety of BDB-001&#xD;
      injection in severe COVID-19 with severe pneumonia, or acute lung injury/acute respiratory&#xD;
      distress syndrome. Patients will be randomized to two treatment arms (Arm A: Conventional&#xD;
      treatment + BDB-001; Arm B: Conventional treatment alone).&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
